information: The company JUNGPFLANZEN CLAUS UND TORSTEN KÜHNE GBR, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1899, which operates in the Vegetables, edible roots and tubers industry. It also operates in the Bedding plants, bulbs and seeds, Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry, Nurseries, and Textile plants industries. It is based in Dresden, Germany.
